This is volume 1 of the Toho Godzilla collection.  The collection was clearly slapped together to make quick buck. You don't get to choose whether you want to watch the movies in the english dub or original Japanese. It is English only. In addition, the collection doesn't start with the original Godzilla movies as both volumes of the set have only movies after 1990. In addition, volume one contains two Mothra movies of which neither involve godzilla in any manner. At the time I purchased these volumes, the included movies weren't listed and i was disappointed by the selection of movies in these sets, but the movies themselves were good, not great, and enjoyable.

For those who want the original and best Japanese versions avoid this useless set which brings nothing new to the films included here.
 those films GODZILLA vs SPACEGODZILLA.....VS DESTOROYAH......VS GING GHIDORAH......VS MOTHRA are the only left Godzilla films from the 90s which were never released in America in their original version with Japanese audio and English subts.
 instead we had already D.F releases exactly with same content like this new release (Godzilla vs spacegodzilla // vs destoroyah)

 So far the only way to get those films separately and with Japanese audio and English subts are the region 3 Asian dvd's which have the longer and best versions of the films.

 Until they release the limited editions of those 4 films in America with the original jap. versions stick to the region 3 dvd's and AVOID THIS RELEASE AT ALL COSTS IF U ARE A TRULLY GODZIILA FAN.

  Godzilla 85 finally released a few days ago in America with the original version now we still wait for the 1991, 1992, 1994 and 1995 films to be released also in that way.

  PS.

 As for the inclusion in the set of the 90s rebirth of mothra series DON'T BOTHER. they are childlish movies and also these are not the original jap. versions as well.
 if u want those movies together with part 3 get the new blu ray which have all 3 movies in their original versions but I don't recommend those movies.
